topic: Book Workflow Series ("Author comparison explorative search")

goals.1: Identify the BGP for obtaining the Italian and French writers who published a book in the last 50 years
goals.2: Compare the number of books written by Italian and French writers
goals.3: Count how many books written by Italian authors are now released with a "public domain" copyright form
goals.4: How many Literature Nobel awards won authors from Italy and from the Kingdom of Italy?
goals.5: Are there books from Litarature Nobel Award winners which are not present in the Vatican Library? (if so, who is the author with more books not in the Vatical Library)?

search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?w ?writerName ?country WHERE { ?w wdt:P106 wd:Q36180; wdt:P166 wd:Q37922; wdt:P27 ?c. ?w <http://schema.org/name> ?writerName. ?c <http://schema.org/name> ?country. FILTER(?c = wd:Q38 || ?c = wd:Q172579). }
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ?p) AS ?subjProps WHERE { wd:Q213678 ?p ?o. }
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ?p) AS ?objProps WHERE { ?s ?p wd:Q213678. }
SELECT ?p ?pname COUNT(DISTINCT ?s) AS ?subjs WHERE { ?s ?p wd:Q213678. ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pname. } GROUP BY ?p ?pname ORDER BY DESC(?subjs)
output: organization directed by the office or position

search_workflow.query: SELECT ?i ?instanceOf COUNT(DISTINCT ?s) AS ?subjs WHERE { ?s wdt:P127|wdt:P276|wdt:P485 wd:Q213678; wdt:P31 ?i. ?i <http://schema.org/name> ?instanceOf. } GROUP BY ?i ?instanceOf ORDER BY DESC(?subjs)

SELECT DISTINCT ?w ?writerName WHERE { ?w wdt:P106 wd:Q36180; wdt:P166 wd:Q37922; wdt:P27 ?c. ?w <http://schema.org/name> ?writerName. FILTER(?c = wd:Q38 || ?c = wd:Q172579). FILTER NOT EXISTS{ ?b wdt:P50 ?w; wdt:P127|wdt:P276|wdt:P485 wd:Q213678; wdt:P31 ?books. FILTER(?books = wd:Q571 || ?books = wd:Q7725634 || ?books = wd:Q47461344). } }

SELECT ?writerName COUNT(DISTINCT ?b) AS ?numberBooks WHERE { ?w wdt:P106 wd:Q36180; wdt:P166 wd:Q37922; wdt:P27 ?c. ?b wdt:P50 ?w; wdt:P31 ?books. ?w <http://schema.org/name> ?writerName. FILTER(?c = wd:Q38 || ?c = wd:Q172579). FILTER(?books = wd:Q571 || ?books = wd:Q7725634 || ?books = wd:Q47461344). FILTER NOT EXISTS{ ?b wdt:P127|wdt:P276|wdt:P485 wd:Q213678. } } GROUP BY ?writerName ORDER BY DESC(?numberBooks) LIMIT 1
